OL,3,C'We might just do it': Brighton
OL,4,Cplayers confident ahead of women's FA
OL,5,CCup final
OL,7,FBrighton and Hove Albion may be
OL,8,Funderdogs in their first-ever women's
OL,9,FFA Cup final against newly-crowned
OL,10,FWomen's Super League champions
OL,11,FManchester City, but their players are
OL,12,Fquietly confident about their chances.
OL,14,FThe Seagulls have already beaten top-
OL,15,Fdivision sides West Ham, Arsenal and
OL,16,FLiverpool to reach the Wembley
OL,17,Fshowpiece, and excitement and
OL,18,Fanticipation are high.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
