PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780078265
OL,3,C'We might just do it': Brighton
OL,4,Cplayers confident ahead of women's FA
OL,5,CCup final
OL,7,FDario Vidosic's side also have
OL,8,Fpositive recent memories of Sunday's
OL,9,Fopponents, beating Manchester City 3-2
OL,10,Fin the league in April.
OL,12,FBrighton had lost their other three
OL,13,Fleague meetings against City since
OL,14,FVidosic took over as manager in July
OL,15,F2024, but they were all single-goal
OL,16,Fdefeats, suggesting a close game is in
OL,17,Fprospect.
OL,19,FCaptain and midfielder Maisie Symonds
OL,20,Fhas been feeling optimistic throughout
OL,21,Fthis season's FA Cup run.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
