PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780078265
OL,3,C'We might just do it': Brighton
OL,4,Cplayers confident ahead of women's FA
OL,5,CCup final
OL,7,FShe said: "I have felt the whole way
OL,8,Falong that we might just do it.
OL,10,F"I feel that we are a very, very good
OL,11,Fcup team because we have the potential
OL,12,Fto beat any side and we've proved that
OL,13,Fdefinitely over the last few months."
OL,15,F"The celebrations after the semi-final
OL,16,Fwere just incredible, an amazing
OL,17,Fmoment for every single one of the
OL,18,Fgirls and they all deserve it."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
