PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780078265
OL,3,C'We might just do it': Brighton
OL,4,Cplayers confident ahead of women's FA
OL,5,CCup final
OL,7,FFellow midfielder Nadine Noordam said
OL,8,Fplaying at Wembley will fulfil a
OL,9,Fchildhood ambition.
OL,11,F"It means a lot, you dream of that as
OL,12,Fa kid, to play at Wembley, that makes
OL,13,Fit even more special.
OL,15,F"It's something special that we've
OL,16,Fachieved, and now we want more of
OL,17,Fcourse."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
