PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780078265
OL,3,C'We might just do it': Brighton
OL,4,Cplayers confident ahead of women's FA
OL,5,CCup final
OL,7,FStriker Carla Camacho echoed her team-
OL,8,Fmate's sentiments, saying: "I think
OL,9,Fit's going to be so exciting, it's
OL,10,Freally, really amazing to play in such
OL,11,Fa big stadium and a good opportunity
OL,12,Ffor memories.
OL,14,FShe added: "It's a special day for
OL,15,Feveryone".
OL,17,FA victory in the Wembley final would
OL,18,Fmark the end of a season which has
OL,19,Fbeen impacted by tragedy.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
