PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780078265
OL,3,C'We might just do it': Brighton
OL,4,Cplayers confident ahead of women's FA
OL,5,CCup final
OL,7,FBrighton's on-field success has been
OL,8,Fmatched by significant off-field
OL,9,Fdevelopments, with the club last month
OL,10,Fannouncing plans for Europe's first
OL,11,Fpurpose-built women's football stadium.
OL,13,FThe stadium would have a minimum
OL,14,Fcapacity of 10,000 and will open no
OL,15,Flater than the 2030/31 season, subject
OL,16,Fto planning approvals from Brighton
OL,17,Fand Hove City Council and Lewes
OL,18,FDistrict Council.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
