OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780078265
OL,3,C'We might just do it': Brighton
OL,4,Cplayers confident ahead of women's FA
OL,5,CCup final
OL,7,FThe club hope that the stadium will
OL,8,Fattract new fans and be welcoming for
OL,9,Ffamilies and first-time attendees.
OL,11,FThey will hoping many of those coming
OL,12,Fto back the team at Wembley will be
OL,13,Fbecome regular visitors to future
OL,14,Fleague games, as the team look to
OL,15,Fbuilt on this season's 7th place
OL,16,Ffinish in the Women's Super League.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
